		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Null modem</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Null_modem.jpg" class="image" title="A null modem adapter"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/Null_modem.jpg/180px-Null_modem.jpg" width="180" height="188" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Null_modem.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
A null modem adapter</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Null modem</b> is a communication method to connect two <a href="/wiki/Data_terminal_equipment" title="Data terminal equipment">DTEs</a> (<a href="/wiki/Computer" title="Computer">computer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Computer_terminal" title="Computer terminal">terminal</a>, <a href="/wiki/Computer_printer" title="Computer printer" class="mw-redirect">printer</a> etc.) directly using a <a href="/wiki/RS-232" title="RS-232">RS-232</a> <a href="/wiki/Serial_cable" title="Serial cable">serial cable</a>. The RS-232 standard is asymmetrical as to the definitions of the two ends of the communications link so it assumes that one end is a DTE and the other is a <a href="/wiki/Data_circuit-terminating_equipment" title="Data circuit-terminating equipment">DCE</a> e.g. a <a href="/wiki/Modem" title="Modem">modem</a>. With a null modem connection the <a href="/wiki/Transmission_(telecommunications)" title="Transmission (telecommunications)">transmit</a> and receive lines are <b>crosslinked</b>. Depending on the purpose, sometimes also one or more <a href="/wiki/Handshaking" title="Handshaking">handshake</a> lines are crosslinked. Several wiring layouts are in use because the null modem connection is not covered by a <a href="/wiki/Standardization" title="Standardization">standard</a>.</p>
